 Garbage、Billy Corgan 和 Ice-T 向已故的 Sinead O'Connor 致敬https://www.nme.com/news/music/sinead-oconnor-irish-music-legend-dies-ged-56-3473863?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=sinead-oconnor-irish-music-legend-dies- 56岁Anagricel DuranWed, 26 Jul 2023 18:15:02 +0000 Music NewsNews..Pop https://www.nme.com/?p=3473863 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Sinead-OConnor-posing.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="2020 年 2 月 9 日，西妮德·奥康纳 (Sinéad O&#39;Connor) 在洛杉矶埃尔雷剧院 (El Rey Theater)。图片来源：Lindsey Best for the Washington Post/GETTY" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Sinead-OConnor-posing.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Sinead-OConnor-posing-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Sinead-OConnor-posing-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Sinead-OConnor-posing-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Sinead-OConnor-posing-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Sinead-OConnor-posing-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这位歌手因翻唱 Prince 的《Nothing Compares 2 U》而享誉全球</p><p><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sinead-oconnor-irish-music-legend-dies-aged-56-3473863">《Garbage》、Billy Corgan 和 Ice-T 主唱向已故 Sinead O&#39;Connor 致敬的帖子</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Sinead-OConnor-posing.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="2020 年 2 月 9 日，西妮德·奥康纳 (Sinéad O&#39;Connor) 在洛杉矶埃尔雷剧院 (El Rey Theater)。图片来源：Lindsey Best for the Washington Post/GETTY" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Sinead-OConnor-posing.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Sinead-OConnor-posing-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Sinead-OConnor-posing-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Sinead-OConnor-posing-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Sinead-OConnor-posing-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Sinead-OConnor-posing-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>著名爱尔兰歌手兼活动家<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sinead-oconnor">西妮德·奥康纳 (Sinéad O&#39;Connor)</a>的家人宣布去世，享年 56 岁。</p><p> “我们怀着极大的悲痛宣布我们敬爱的西妮德去世。她的家人和朋友都很伤心，并在这个非常困难的时刻要求隐私。” <a href="https://www.theguardian.com/music/2023/jul/26/sinead-oconnor-dies-aged-56" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《卫报》报道了这位歌手家人的一份声明。</em></a></p><p>她去世的消息是在她<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sinead-oconnor-pays-tribute-to-17-year-old-son-following-his-death-3132870">17 岁的儿子肖恩 (Shane) 于 2022 年 1 月自杀</a>一年后传出的。她最后的社交媒体帖子是一条推文，上面贴着她已故儿子的照片，标题是：“从那时起，我就一直像不死的夜间生物一样生活。他是我一生的挚爱，我灵魂的灯。”</p><p>死因尚未公布。 </p><figure id="attachment_3473869" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3473869" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3473869" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Sinead-OConnor-Photo-by-SGranitz_WireImage.jpg" alt="西妮德·奥康纳。图片来源：SGranitz/GETTY" width="2000" height="1368" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Sinead-OConnor-Photo-by-SGranitz_WireImage.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Sinead-OConnor-Photo-by-SGranitz_WireImage-218x150.jpg 218w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Sinead-OConnor-Photo-by-SGranitz_WireImage-400x274.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Sinead-OConnor-Photo-by-SGranitz_WireImage-800x547.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Sinead-OConnor-Photo-by-SGranitz_WireImage-696x476.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Sinead-OConnor-Photo-by-SGranitz_WireImage-1392x952.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Sinead-OConnor-Photo-by-SGranitz_WireImage-1068x731.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3473869" class="wp-caption-text">西妮德·奥康纳。图片来源：SGranitz/GETTY</figcaption></figure><p> 1966 年 12 月 8 日，她出生于都柏林，原名西妮德·玛丽·伯纳黛特·奥康纳 (Sinéad Marie Bernadette O&#39;Connor)，她在 80 年代末凭借首张专辑《The Lion And The Cobra》而声名鹊起。</p><p>在她的整个职业生涯中，奥康纳发行了 10 张录音室专辑，其中她翻唱的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/prince">Prince</a>的《Nothing Compares 2 U》获得了全世界的赞誉，并于同年登上<em><a href="https://www.billboard.com/artist/sinead-oconnor/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">公告牌百强单曲</a></em>榜第一名。</p><p>她对这首歌的演绎在全球排行榜上名列前茅，并为她赢得了三项格莱美提名。这首歌曲的标志性伴奏视频由英国电影制片人约翰·梅伯里 (John Maybury) 执导，与歌曲本身一样出名。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Sinéad O&#39;Connor - Nothing Compares 2 U（官方音乐视频）[高清]" width="696" height="522" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/0-EF60neguk?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>奥康纳随后<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sinead-oconnor-says-prince-attacked-her-at-his-hollywood-home-2943836">与普林斯本人发生争执，她在接受<em>《纽约时报》</em>采访时声称</a>，在凭借《Nothing Compares 2 U》获得成功后，她在普林斯家中与这位音乐家发生了暴力冲突。</p><p>社交媒体上的粉丝和名人纷纷向这位歌手致敬。</p><p> <em>《古战场传奇》</em>主演凯特丽娜·巴尔夫 (Caitríona Balfe) 在她的 Instagram 页面上发布了一张奥康纳的照片，并配文写道：“我希望你平安……并与你的男婴在一起。感谢您与我们分享您的灵魂，并用您令人难以置信的声音来安慰我们，美丽的西妮德。安息吧。”</p><p> <a href="/artists/garbage">Garbage</a>在 Twitter 上分享了这位歌手的照片，并配文：“我心碎了”。</p><p> <a href="/artists/the-smashing-pumpkins">Smashing Pumpkins</a>主唱比利·科根<a href="/artists/billy-corgan">(Billy Corgan)</a>也在他的 Instagram 上分享了这位爱尔兰歌手的照片，并配文写道：“我对西尼德有一点了解，是在她的一场演出中认识的，后来当她住在沃克家时，我认识了她。”芝加哥郊外的家。”</p><p>他继续说道：“她非常诚实、可爱又有趣，她在某些方面很有才华，我不确定她是否完全理解。但西尼德是我们这一代人中独一无二的人物，她始终忠实于内在和外在的尖锐声音。为此，我将永远钦佩和尊重她。永远不要忘记，她曾经因为一次简单的抵抗行为而被取消。她的罪行？撕掉一张照片。”</p><p>说唱歌手<a href="/artists/ice-t">Ice-T</a>在推特上对她的分享表示敬意：“向 Sinead 致敬……她代表着某种东西……与大多数人不同……安息吧……”</p><p>以下是对这位传奇爱尔兰歌手的更多致敬： </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/CvK5wcisbLN/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.886,41.1 524.886,50 C524.886,58.899 532.1,66.113 541,66.113 C549.9,66.113 557.115,58.899 557.115,50 C557.115,41.1 549.9,33.886 541,33.886 M565.378,62.101 C565.244,65.022 564.756,66.606 564.346,67.663 C563.803,69.06